NAME Console Hello
DESCRIPTION Writes HELLO! into output console module 2 then halts.

# Constants
WORD 0 0x48   # H
WORD 1 0x45   # E
WORD 2 0x4C   # L
WORD 3 0x4F   # O
WORD 4 0x21   # !

# Program
INSTR 40 LDA R0 M0 0
INSTR 39 STA R0 M2 0
INSTR 38 LDA R0 M0 1
INSTR 37 STA R0 M2 1
INSTR 36 LDA R0 M0 2
INSTR 35 STA R0 M2 2
INSTR 34 LDA R0 M0 2
INSTR 33 STA R0 M2 3
INSTR 32 LDA R0 M0 3
INSTR 31 STA R0 M2 4
INSTR 30 LDA R0 M0 4
INSTR 29 STA R0 M2 5
INSTR 28 HLT R0 R0 R0
